    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable daily driver for several years. The exterior shows some age with minor scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior has typical wear on the upholstery and a few stains on the carpet. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few months. It's a solid choice for someone looking for dependable transportation at an affordable price point, provided they don't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
      "price": 19500.0,
