    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule of pure elegance. Imagine gliding through the coastal fog, the engine's purr a low, confident hum that resonates in your chest. The deep sapphire paint reflects the world like a still lake at twilight, while the hand-stitched leather interior welcomes you like a familiar embrace. Every curve of this machine was designed for the romantic who views the road as a canvas. It carries the soul of a bygone era of craftsmanship, waiting for its next curator to continue its story.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
